OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FThe public is being asked to put
OL,7,Fforward names for the next Archbishop
OL,8,Fof Canterbury, after Justin Welby
OL,9,Fresigned over safeguarding failings.
OL,11,FHis replacement will be the 106th
OL,12,Fperson to hold the role ` the most
OL,13,Fsenior bishop of the Church of England
OL,14,Fand the spiritual leader of the
OL,15,Fworldwide Anglican Communion.
