OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FThe public consultation on the
OL,7,Fappointment process for a new
OL,8,FArchbishop of Canterbury "is an
OL,9,Fopportunity to gather the views of a
OL,10,Fwide range of people from across
OL,11,FEngland and the Anglican Communion on
OL,12,Fthe gifts, qualities and skills
OL,13,Fneeded" for the role, the Church said.
OL,15,FMr Welby stepped down following the
OL,16,Fpublication of the Makin Review, a
OL,17,Fdamning report into prolific sexual
OL,18,Fabuser John Smyth.
