OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FThe independent investigation,
OL,7,Fpublished in November, found the
OL,8,FChristian camp leader and barrister
OL,9,Fattacked as many as 130 boys and young
OL,10,Fmen, including at Christian summer
OL,11,Fcamps. It concluded that, had Mr Welby
OL,12,Fformally reported it to police a
OL,13,Fdecade ago, Smyth might have been
OL,14,Fbrought to justice.
OL,16,FSmyth died aged 75 in Cape Town in
OL,17,F2018 while still under investigation
OL,18,Fby Hampshire Police.
