OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FPeople will be able to submit names
OL,7,Ffor Mr Welby's replacement to the
OL,8,FCrown Nominations Commission (CNC) `
OL,9,Fthe body charged with nominating the
OL,10,Fnew archbishop.
OL,12,FHowever, there will be no advert in
OL,13,Fwhich anyone can submit their name for
OL,14,Fthe position of new Archbishop.
OL,15,FInstead, possible candidates will be
OL,16,F"invited in" to the process.
