OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FThe Bishop of Liverpool Right Reverend
OL,7,FDr John Perumbalath stepped down from
OL,8,Fhis role in January following
OL,9,Fallegations of sexual assault and
OL,10,Fharassment.
OL,12,FChannel 4 News reported that the
OL,13,Fsenior bishop has been accused of
OL,14,Fsexual misconduct by two women,
OL,15,Fincluding another bishop, which he has
OL,16,Fdenied.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
