OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FOne woman accused Dr Perumbalath of
OL,7,Fkissing her without consent and
OL,8,Fgroping her, and a female bishop
OL,9,Faccused him of sexual harassment. Both
OL,10,Fincidents allegedly took place in
OL,11,FEssex in 2023.
OL,13,FStephen Cottrell, the Archbishop of
OL,14,FYork, has temporarily taken over from
OL,15,Fthe Archbishop of Canterbury.
