OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FBut in December there were calls for
OL,7,Fhim to resign over his handling of a
OL,8,Fsex abuse case. A BBC investigation
OL,9,Freported that Mr Cottrell allegedly
OL,10,Flet priest David Tudor stay in post in
OL,11,Fthe diocese, despite knowing he had
OL,12,Fbeen barred from being alone with
OL,13,Fchildren, and had paid compensation to
OL,14,Fa sexual abuse victim.
OL,16,FCottrell, the Church's second-most-
OL,17,Fsenior bishop, responded to the report
OL,18,Fin a personal statement, saying he was
OL,19,F"deeply sorry we were not able to take
OL,20,Faction earlier".
