OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FThe Church said the CNC will "use the
OL,7,Fthemes that emerge through this
OL,8,F(public consultation) process to
OL,9,Finform the commission on the needs of
OL,10,Fthe mission of the Church of England
OL,11,Fand the wider Anglican Communion".
OL,13,FThe consultation will run until Friday
OL,14,FMarch 28.
OL,16,FFull membership of the CNC is expected
OL,17,Fto be known next month, with a first
OL,18,Fmeeting planned for May, and two
OL,19,Fothers in July and September.
