OL,3,CPublic invited to name next Archbishop
OL,4,Cof Canterbury after series of scandals
OL,6,FThe commission will agree on a "role
OL,7,Fprofile" and "person specification"
OL,8,Ffor the next archbishop of Canterbury
OL,9,Fand put together a longlist and
OL,10,Fshortlist. It is not thought names of
OL,11,Fpotential candidates will be
OL,12,Fofficially made public during the
OL,13,Fprocess.
OL,15,FUsually, the name of the CNC's
OL,16,Frecommended candidate is given to the
OL,17,Fprime minister who passes it to the
OL,18,Fmonarch, and it is expected there
OL,19,Fcould be an announcement by autumn.
